              "name": "Two Actions",
              "subtype": "action_type",
              "type": "stat_block_section"
            },
            "effect": "Kerrdremak whispers under his breath, and one adjacent enemy must attempt a DC 17 Will save or become frightened 1 as they hear a whispering voice just behind them that claims to know when the target will die; the target is then temporarily immune to Whispering Retreat for 1 hour. Kerrdremak then Strides, and this movement doesn't trigger reactions from frightened creatures. He must end this movement in a space that isn't adjacent to any enemy",
            "links": [
              {
                "alt": "frightened 1",
                "aonid": 19,
                "game-obj": "Conditions",
                "name": "frightened 1",
                "type": "link"
              }
            ],
            "name": "Whispering Retreat",
            "requirement": "Kerrdremak is adjacent to at least one enemy",
            "saving_throw": [
              {
                "dc": 17,
